.TH ABRAFLEXI-MATCH-BANK 1 "July 17, 2026" "abraflexi-matcher" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
abraflexi-match-bank \- Match a single incoming bank payment to its issued invoice in AbraFlexi
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B abraflexi-match-bank
.RI [ DOCUMENTID ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B abraflexi-match-bank
matches one specific incoming bank payment record, identified by
.IR DOCUMENTID
(AbraFlexi banka document code or numeric ID), against issued invoices,
using AbraFlexi's own bank-matching logic.
.PP
.I DOCUMENTID
may be given as the first command-line argument, or via the
.B DOCUMENTID
environment variable. If neither is set, the script logs an error and
exits without matching anything.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.RI [ DOCUMENTID ]
AbraFlexi banka document code or numeric ID to match. Overrides the
.B DOCUMENTID
environment variable when given.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B DOCUMENTID
AbraFlexi banka document code or numeric ID to match, used when no
command-line argument is given.
.TP
.B RESULT_FILE
Path to the output JSON report file.
.TP
.B MATCHER_LOCALIZE
Locale for log/report messages: en_US (default), cs_CZ, or sk_SK.
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_URL
AbraFlexi server URL
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_LOGIN
AbraFlexi login username
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_PASSWORD
AbraFlexi password
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_COMPANY
AbraFlexi company code
.SH FILES
.TP
.I match_report.json
Default output file containing
.I matched
and
.I unmatched
arrays with the payment document code, in JSON format compliant with the multiflexi report schema.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR abraflexi-match-received-payment (1),
.BR abraflexi-matcher-in (1),
.BR abraflexi-matcher (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Written by Vitex Software.
